Summary: Kept going up through to the stratospere,
divs: Sighting DetailsIt was the approx date, Sept 68. Mother and family saw this over the ocean. Cylindrical object over the ocean was seen and it appearsed to go up and up had a light on top, glowed out. That's all the info I can give without consulting my mother first.
